import React from "react"; import axios from "axios"; import { TodoType } from "./todo"; import TableTwo from "./TableTwo"; import { Fragment, useRef, useState, useEffect } from "react"; import { Dialog, Transition } from "@headlessui/react"; const Table = () => { const [newTodo, setNewTodo] = useState({ kullaniciAd: "", kullaniciSoyad: "", kullaniciEmail: "", yasadigiSehir: "", }); const handleInputChange=(e:any)=>{ setNewTodo({ ...newTodo, [e.target.name]:e.target.value, }) } const [data, setData] = useState([]); const [open, setOpen] = useState(true) // const cancelButtonRef =useRef(null); const fetchData = async () => { try { const response = await axios.get("http://localhost:9363/post/panel"); setData(response.data.slice(0, 5)); // slice işlemini burada gerçekleştirin } catch (error) { console.error("Error fetching data:", error); } }; useEffect(() => { fetchData(); }); const EventClick = async (e: any, id: any) => { e.preventDefault(); try { await axios.delete(`http://localhost:9363/post/panel/${id}`); setData((prevTodos) => prevTodos.filter((todo) => todo.id !== id)); // Silinen öğeyi filtreleyerek veriyi güncelle } catch (error) { console.error("Veri alınırken hata oluştu:", error); } }; const Click = () => { setOpen(true); }; return ( <>
{data.map((item, index) => { return ( EventClick(e, item.id)} /> ); })}
